PrecisAppointment of ANTHONY WHITFORD of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, to be Deputy Commissioner of the Northwest Territories to execute the office and functions of the Commissioner during her absence or illness or other inability or when the office of Commissioner is vacant, for a term of three years.
